VAMPIRE VAMPIRES "VAMPIRE SKILL"

Vampire (skill)

The Vampire skill tree contains all the powers of these creatures of the night.
Vampirism is not a curse, per se, but its powers do come at a price: vampires
must drink blood. Vampires are not harmed by the sun, but their powers do not
function in broad daylight.

Vampires at skill level 15 or bellow are constantly hungry, losing a blood
point ever hour even if they have no blood powers active. At such low levels,
these vampires gain skill just by drinking the blood of others. Higher level
vampires have an hourly upkeep based only on which powers are active. See the
help file on BITE for more information on drinking blood.

To become a vampire, seek out another of their kind -- if you dare.

Check out &yHELP VAMPIRE GUIDE&0 for a getting-started.

See also: BITE, SIRE, FEED, BOOST, ALACRITY, BLOOD FORTITUDE, MUMMIFY,
    TASTE BLOOD, ANCIENT BLOOD, BLOODSWORD, COMMAND, MAJESTY, SUMMON, SOULMASK,
    DEATHSHROUD, WOLF FORM, HORRID FORM, MIST FORM, CLAWS, PREADTOR VISION,
    REGENERATE, BUILD HAVEN, DAYWALKING, VEINTAP, WEAKEN, BAT FORM,
    UNNATURAL THIRST, SANGUINE RESTORATION
