BLOODSWORD "BLOOD-RED SWORD"

Bloodsword (Vampire ability)

Usage:  bloodsword
Cost: 20 blood

A vampire with this ability can create a sword from its own blood. The blood-
red sword is only as powerful as the vampire who created it, and it only lasts
a short time.

When you activate this power, you will automatically wield the sword.
